                  <li>Relevant server-side programming languages (C# .NET)</li>
                  <li>SQL and NoSQL database solutions (AWS Redshift and AWS DynamoDB)</li>
                  <li>Big data processing frameworks and concepts </li>
                  <li>DevOps practices</li>
